questions.question:
What does the following code do?

var a, b: integer;
begin
  a := a + b;
  b := a - b;
  a := a - b;
end;

A. exchanges a and b
B. doubles a and stores in b
C. doubles b and stores in a
D. leaves a and b unchanged
E. none of the above

What function of x, n is computed by this program?

Function what(x, n: integer): integer;
Var value: integer;
begin
  value := 1;
  if n > 0 then
  begin
    if n mod 2 = 1 then
      value := value * x;
    value := value * what(x*x, n div 2)
  end;
  what := value
end;

A. x^n
B. x^(n/2)
C. x^(2n)
D. None of the above
